PpyMilter
=========

$Id: README 21 2008-08-08 18:31:02Z codewhale $

PpyMilter is a mail filtering API implementing the Sendmail milter protocol
in pure Python.  It is the python equivalent of "Sendmail::PMilter".  This
library allows MTAs implementing the milter API to filter and modify mail
in transit during the SMTP connection.


